(1)
9 Westchester Square (Lane Ave.), at the N.E. corner of Overing Street, showing the Huntington Free Library and Reading Room. This old section of the library is actually adjoining the corner, while the new addition extends to the corner.

P. L. Sperr.

(2)
The same, showing a side view.

P. L. Sperr.

(3)
The same, at a later date, including the new addition. The view is from underneath the elevated structure of the I.R.T. Pelham Bay Park subway line.

P. L. Sperr.
